            &#x2022;
            <b>
              performance feedback
            </b>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <b>
              Middle managers need training in
            </b>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>
            &#x2022;
            <b>
              designing and implementing effective group and intergroup work and
              information systems
            </b>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>
            &#x2022;
            <b>
              defining and monitoring group-level performance indicators
            </b>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
